# Brief Service — LLM Configuration
# Drop this file in your project root or in .briefs/
# Pick ONE provider and fill in the values below.

# ── OpenRouter (recommended — one key, every model) ──────────
# 1. Go to https://openrouter.ai/keys
# 2. Create a free API key
# 3. Uncomment and fill in:
#
# BRIEF_LLM_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here
# BRIEF_LLM_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
# BRIEF_LLM_MODEL=anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet

# ── OpenAI (direct) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# BRIEF_LLM_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# ── Ollama (local, free) ─────────────────────────────────────
# BRIEF_LLM_API_KEY=ollama
# BRIEF_LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1
# BRIEF_LLM_MODEL=llama3

# ── Groq (fast, free tier) ───────────────────────────────────
# BRIEF_LLM_API_KEY=gsk_...
# BRIEF_LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.groq.com/openai/v1
# BRIEF_LLM_MODEL=llama-3.1-70b-versatile
